$interpreted: Slave Supervisor: You're not the one to talk! You're the one who beat him half to death! He's going to have to heal for weeks before being able to walk again!
Slave Supervisor: I'll be taking over for him today. Let's go.
Slave Supervisor: You must really hate him to have beat him so bad.
Thug: Poor things, so disfigured they can't even work as slaves. Forced to act like monkeys just to make a buck.
Sophie: Hey! We work hard at our jobs, what's it got to...
Rune: Hey, you can't do that!
Sophie: Rune, do you want to see some magic?
Sophie: Quick, stand on the ball.
Spectator: This is spectacular! Hey! You guys! Come check this out!!
Sophie: The sound of laughter, works every time!
Sophie: And now, the event you've all been waiting for——
Amazed Spectator: Whaaa～scared me off my socks! She got balls!
Awestruck Spectator: And look at that fellow～what muscles～
Child Spectator: Hey, you two are amazing!
Excited Spectator: Yay! Yayy! One more time! Encore! Encore!
Sophie: Finally got you to smile～
Sophie: Yeah, that's what you call what's on your face.
Sophie: As long as you're smiling, you'll have the courage to face the future.
Slave Supervisor: Rune! I've been looking for you all over!
Slave Supervisor: Rune, you'd best be coming with me.
Sophie: Ah, you're meeting with a friend? Well then, see you later! Rune, don't forget to smile!
